These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  electrician, entrepreneur, mechanic, paramedic, photographer, social-worker, videographer
There are 7 different favourite beverages: cola, tea, fanta, hot-chocolate, sprite, mirinda, iced-tea
 1. the paramedic is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 2. the person drinking sprite is the paramedic##1
 3. the videographer is on the right of the social-worker##1
 4. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
 5. the mechanic is in the middle##1
 6. the person drinking cola is on the far left##1
 7. the photographer is the person drinking cola##1
 8. the electrician is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
 9. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the mechanic##1
11. the videographer is on the right of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| Job           | photographer | paramedic | entrepreneur | mechanic | electrician | social-worker | videographer |
| Beverage   | cola    | sprite   | hot-chocolate      | mirinda | fanta    | tea    | iced-tea         |

