.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-2::.
There 7 different types of food: cranberry, cucumber, eggplant, nectarine, peach, raspberry, watermelon
7 different games are played: mah-jongg, go, chess, backgammon, canasta, snooker, scrabble
 1. the person playing canasta is the person eating nectarine##1
 2. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
 3. the person playing snooker is on the far right##1
 4. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person playing go##1
 5. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
 6. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
 7. the person playing canasta is in the middle##1
 8. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person eating peach##1
 9. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
10. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7     |
| Food          | cranberry | cucumber | peach | nectarine | raspberry | watermelon | eggplant |
| Game   | go      | chess   | backgammon   | canasta      | mah-jongg       | scrabble       | snooker     |

