.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-3::.
There 7 different types of food: corn, cucumber, lemon, lettuce, onion, pepper, spinach
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: trance, d&b, salsa, disco, dubstep, rock, gospel
 1. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the person eating onion##1
 2. the person eating onion is on the left of the fan of gospel##1
 3. the fan of d&b is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
 4. the person eating corn is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
 5. the fan of trance is the person eating onion##1
 6. the fan of salsa is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
 7. the fan of d&b is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
 8. the fan of d&b is on the right of the fan of disco##1
 9. the person eating pepper is the fan of disco##1
10. the person eating lemon is on the right of the fan of trance##1
11. the fan of disco is in the middle##1
12. the person eating spinach is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |     7     |
| Food   | cucumber | onion     | lemon  | pepper       | corn       | spinach  | lettuce   |
| Music-Genre    | rock  | trance | gospel | disco | d&b | salsa | dubstep |

