 3. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
 4. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1
 5. the person eating pear is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
 7. the person drinking iced-tea is in the middle##1
 8. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person eating radish##1
 9. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person eating pear##1
10. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |  3  |    4     |    5    |   6   |      7      |
| Beverage    | coffee | soy-milk   | 7up | iced-tea | sprite  | juice | almond-milk |
| Food   | kale   | radish | artichoke | broccoli     | pumpkin | pear | mango   |

