.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-9::.
There 7 different types of food: broccoli, corn, grapes, kiwi, papaya, radish, watermelon
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: september, february, october, november, april, august, july
 1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 3. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person eating papaya##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in september is in the middle##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in november is the person eating broccoli##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in april is the person eating radish##1
 7. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 9. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person eating corn##1
10. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
11. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person eating radish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2     |   3    |    4     |   5    |     6      |   7    |
| Food        | corn | broccoli | grapes | kiwi     | radish | watermelon | papaya |
| Birthday   | august | november  | july    | september | april | february       | october   |

